{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase the minimum age to purchase paint aerosols to 18",
        "additional_details": "We believe the benefits of allowing youths between 16-18 to buy spray paint aerosols do not outweigh the cost and effort of removing graffiti and the risks of sniffing aerosols. Many States in USA have a minimum age of 18.",
        "background": "Increase the law on the age for buying paint aerosols to 18 years old.",
